      "text": "私、まだ結婚するつもりなんてないからね！",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だいたい、誰からのプロポーズなの！？",
      "startTime": 4.6666667699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈……。誤解だ\n頼むから、俺の話を聞いてくれ",
      "startTime": 11.2999998807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-09.m4a",
      "text": "嫌！　{user}くんの話なんて",
      "startTime": 13.8999782324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "聞きたくない！　結婚だってしないんだから！",
      "startTime": 16.6333128373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、分かったから、頼む……！\n俺の説明が悪かった！",
      "startTime": 23.6666692178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "結婚じゃなくて、麻奈を広告塔にしたウエディング企画\nなんだ。インタビューやCM、グラビア撮影の仕事だよ",
      "startTime": 29.5000025511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-04.m4a",
      "text": "へ？　……仕事？　ウエディング、の？",
      "startTime": 34.4560802063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-04.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、へぇ……そう、なんだ？",
      "startTime": 39.0227446476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-02.m4a",
      "text": "紛らわしい言い方するから勘違いしちゃった",
      "startTime": 44.5227472542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sorry-01.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと聞かずに騒いじゃってごめんね",
      "startTime": 49.756081695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-11.m4a",
      "text": "でもさっきのは{user}くんが悪いよ！",
      "startTime": 54.556085165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
